## mediationverse — Ecosystem Meta-Package

**Version**: 0.0.0.9000 (dev; not yet on CRAN)

Meta-package that loads the core mediation ecosystem: `medfit`, `probmed`,
`RMediation`, `medrobust`, `medsim`.

---

## CRAN Status by Dependency

| Package | CRAN | Notes |
|---------|------|-------|
| medfit | ✅ 0.2.0+ | Dropped from `Remotes`; pinned in `Imports (>= 0.2.0)` |
| RMediation | ✅ 1.5.0 | Released 2026-06-18 |
| probmed | ❌ | Still GitHub-only |
| medsim | ❌ | Still in `Remotes: Data-Wise/medsim` |
| medrobust | ❌ | Still in `Remotes: Data-Wise/medrobust` |

